        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — MRL 5 CFD solver",
        "description": "CFD solver must be under formal version control (Git-tagged releases), must have a documented unit-test suite with ≥95% pass rate on regression suite, and must carry an FDA-recognized software validation report or equivalent IEC 62304 documentation. All simulation scripts must be archived in a traceable repository with run-environment metadata."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2 is operated under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Regression suite (847 tests) achieved 100% pass at the tagged release. FDA Pre-Sub Q-submission software validation report (K231045-SWV) on file. All simulation input decks and environment metadata archived in institutional GitLab under tag cou2-final-v1.0."
