        "description": "Simulation analysts must have documented training in CFD for cardiovascular devices (minimum 2 years experience or equivalent training record). Simulation setup must be independently reviewed by a second qualified analyst. Boundary condition application must be verified against the validation plan."
      },
      "rationale": "Lead analyst (5 years CFD experience in cardiovascular devices, ASME V&V 40 training certificate 2023). Independent review conducted by senior analyst (12 years experience) per internal procedure SOP-CFD-007. Boundary condition audit confirmed all five operating points matched validation plan VP-COU2-2024 within specified tolerances."
    },
    {
