      },
      "rationale": "Input equivalency table (Table 4, VP-COU2-2024) documents simulation vs. experimental values for all primary inputs at all five operating points. Maximum deviation: flow rate 0.6% (within ±2% criterion), rotor speed 3 RPM (within ±10 RPM criterion), viscosity 0.05 mPa·s (within measurement uncertainty). All inputs confirmed equivalent within acceptance bounds."
